# Report & Prompting Format

## File naming

```
Report/{NN}-{phase-slug}-report.md
Prompting/{NN}-{phase-slug}-transcript.md
```

- `{NN}`: two digits (01, 02, 03, 05 — skip 04)
- Same `{NN}` and `{phase-slug}` for report and transcript pairs

## Report header (required)

```markdown
# {NN} — {Phase Title} — Report

| Item | Value |
|------|-------|
| Step | {NN} |
| Phase | ... |
| Branch | `...` |
| Method | Dual-Track TDD #1 (Outside-In) |
| Date | YYYY-MM-DD |
| Status | In Progress / Complete |
```

Include: goals, work done, test results, checklist, next step.

## Transcript header (required)

```markdown
# {NN} — {Phase Title} — Transcript

| Item | Value |
|------|-------|
| Step | {NN} |
| Phase | ... |
| Branch | `...` |
| Exported | YYYY-MM-DD |
| Source | Cursor Agent Transcript |
```

Body: `## Turn N — User` / `## Turn N — Assistant` sections; omit tool-call noise when readable.

## Index files

Update `Report/00-index.md` and `Prompting/00-index.md` when a phase completes.
